match.about:
Payment info 
Venmo @buckskinhillsprc13

Please select the appropriate division so that trophies handed out will go smoothly. 

Location:
4796 East Diamond Mt. Highway Vernal, Utah 84078
Match Director-Trace Thacker
Check in and zero begins @ 7:30am-8:30am. Shooters will also be able to shoot out to other distances as well.

At check in shooters will have to sign a county waiver (as per county) quick and easy! It can also be submitted on the buckskinhills.com. One time per year! 

Match description and safety brief @ 8:45 am
Match starts @ 9:00 am 80-90 rounds for score
Target distance 300-1200 yards
This match is for new shooters and experienced shooters.
All rifleman are invited and welcome to participate. There will be test your ability stages so come prepared for NOT ONLY PRONE!

Match Fee is $45
We will be taking Venmo as payment please Venmo
@buckskinhillsprc13
for comment put your full name and date of match. It will help us keep track of who has and has not paid. If you do not pay prior to the match you will not be allowed to shoot.
